          "description": "I did not have a good experience getting my wisdom teeth removed here.\n\nI went with Dr. Tchoi in 2022 after seeing some good reviews online. We agreed to remove 3 of my wisdom teeth, including one that was not fully out. While Dr. Tchoi told me the removal was successful, I noticed significant pain in my inner cheek. He had hit it during surgery. To this day, I get 4-5 mouth ulcers/year specifically in that area and nowhere else. We're talking right in the middle of my cheek, nowhere near where the tooth extraction should have been.\n\nI hope other people will have a better experience. I certainly will not come back.",
